headline: DuPont Completes Separation of Qnity Electronics
summary: DuPont (NYSE: DD) today announced that it completed the separation of its electronics business into an independent public company, Qnity Electronics, Inc. ("Qnity"), on November 1, 2025. DuPont shares will continue to trade on the New York Stock Exchange under the symbol "DD" and, effective today, Qnity will begin "regular way" trading on the New York Stock Exchange under the symbol "Q".
